a035e7efcec6207652552ac6454ad","tid":1636528,"uid":54557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"我唔知呢班所謂醫生係咩邏輯<br />\n事實係黑警向左邊胸部開槍<br />\n理得佢中肺定心<br />\n總之就係左邊胸部<br />\n而有常識嘅人都知9成9嘅人但心都係左邊<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n同埋重點係 射中肺只係好彩 唔代表個黑警唔係對住個心黎射<br />\n事後射唔中心緊係講乜都得<br />\n就算中左咪又係兜話原本想射落啲 點知有偏差<br />\n<br />\n仲有樣嘢 真係要形容位置嘅話 我個人會用鎖骨對上嘅兩邊先叫膊頭附近<br />\n鎖骨以下一律叫心口左/右/中間"},{"pid":"53ec9b0ebb8db6fb02795d2f9f5a44b99e004d1a","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"其實心既APEX都去到你粒LIN下面<br />\n可能呢位仁兄個心特別細啦 要用人眼X光先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fbc9e321fc8f2ae8518c260376cd474fd53833","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e87f31c4d646226e894846bfaaf263b53e62dac5","tid":1636528,"uid":9846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:58:24.000Z","msg":"差少少block埋樓主，btw負皮比篇文"},{"pid":"cd118de6ecbb24f1c74725404ae65301d566dec8","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87f31c4d646226e894846bfaaf263b53e62dac5","tid":1636528,"uid":9846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:58:24.000Z","msg":"差少少block埋樓主，btw負皮比篇文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:00:20.000Z","msg":"負皮就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和勇一家 遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa991f9cb78e1404c4f617a7071029caedc2d16a","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a80b8ac2e2388a6b516b30a97f6c614b6b2e0da","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83eee2c28e31cd6fe5d4b227bb6a72149a4cd988","tid":1636528,"uid":103870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cde53179d22b57001b9ebd845b75230e0e0763c","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9359f4fb1d02f45e6e9f02044dd7b9410839661","tid":1636528,"uid":247526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}